"description":"Today in History is the BEST way to get key facts about iconic global events and fun facts from across the centuries, delivered right to your mobile device. Our reminders will make sure you're never out of the loop.\n\nCreated for History, trivia, and knowledge lovers. Get all the important events of the day or narrow your selection down to one of our specific categories: Events, Births, Deaths, Holidays, and more…\n\nWe bring you the most important, epic, and memorable moments in History.\n\n*** Find wisdom in quotes from historical figures.\n\n*** Immerse yourself in the images that capture historical events as they happened.\n\n*** Feel the emotion of the headlines that made the world stop and take notice.\n\nBy experiencing historical events from a variety of angles, you'll gain a new perspective on their importance and new insights into the people who shaped the history of our world.\n\n----- GREAT FUN FOR EVERYONE -----\n\n· Check it in the morning to get your brain pumping to start the day!\n· Post your favorite fun facts to blogs and social media for inspiration and perspective!\n· Share your favorite events and educate your friends and family!\n· Challenge coworkers and friends with historical trivia!\n\n----- TOP FEATURES -----\n\n· Quote of the day: Timeless wisdom from iconic historical figures.\n· Images: Visual representation of every event, headline, and Quote.\n· Headlines: Details on significant events that have shaped our world.\n\n----- PRO -----\n\nFor the ultimate history fans, we are adding the ability to support the future development of TIH and other educational products with our TIH Pro subscription, only $1.99/month.\n\nEven if you don't subscribe, we appreciate your support. You inspire us to make more great apps like Today in History!Even if you don't subscribe we appreciate your support greatly. You inspire us to make more great apps like Today in History!", "genres":["Education", "Reference"], "userRatingCount":90}]
